ANDROID ENVIRONMENT SETUP
==================================
1. Download sdk;
2. Set PATH to sdk/tools, sdk/platform-tools;
     (modify PATH variable in ~/.bashrc, source .bashrc, export PATH)
3. Install API from sdk/platform-tools/android; Need to install system images too;
4. Open Virtual Device Manager, Create new device;
5. Run 'emulator @nexus4' to start. (nexus4 is name of the virtual device);


BUILDING APPLICATION
==================================
1. Download source code;
2. edit local.properties file, set sdk.dir;
3. type 'ant release' to build;
4. Start the emulator 'emulator @nexus4';
5. Enter 'bin' directory, type 'adb install xxx.apk'
6. Type 'ant clean' to clean the build.
